OL,3,CUK could see hottest ever day in May
OL,4,Cas 33C forecast for bank holiday Monday
OL,6,FThe UK is forecast to see its hottest
OL,7,Fever day in May over the bank holiday
OL,8,Fweekend, with temperatures expected to
OL,9,Fbe above 30C.
OL,11,FHeat health alerts have been issued
OL,12,Ffor much of the Midlands, eastern
OL,13,FEngland and the South East ahead of a
OL,14,Fheatwave.
OL,16,FHighs of 28C are expected in parts of
OL,17,Fsouth-east England on Friday before
OL,18,Fclimbing above 30C across swathes of
OL,19,FEngland and Wales over the following
OL,20,Fdays.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
