PN,31102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1779620575
OL,3,CUK could see hottest ever day in May
OL,4,Cas 33C forecast for bank holiday Monday
OL,6,FIt means many areas will also be
OL,7,Fhotter than top European holiday spots
OL,8,Fincluding Mykonos, Marbella and
OL,9,FBenidorm.
OL,11,FMet Office deputy chief forecaster,
OL,12,FSteve Kocher, said: "It is likely that
OL,13,Fthe May and spring UK temperature
OL,14,Frecords will be broken over the bank
OL,15,Fholiday weekend, with forecast
OL,16,Ftemperatures surpassing the existing
OL,17,Frecord of 32.8C."
OL,19,FTemperatures are forecast to reach 33C
OL,20,Fin southern England and the Midlands
OL,21,Fon Monday.
