OL,3,CUK could see hottest ever day in May
OL,4,Cas 33C forecast for bank holiday Monday
OL,6,FThe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,7,Fyellow alerts come into force on
OL,8,FFriday morning, with officials warning
OL,9,Fthat the hot weather could cause minor
OL,10,Fdisruption to health and social care
OL,11,Fservices through to Wednesday.
OL,13,FVulnerable people may need extra
OL,14,Fsupport, with hotter indoor
OL,15,Ftemperatures also expected, according
OL,16,Fto the UKHSA.
OL,18,FParts of Scotland and Northern Ireland
OL,19,Fare forecast to see temperatures
OL,20,Freaching the mid-20s by next week.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
