OL,3,CUK could see hottest ever day in May
OL,4,Cas 33C forecast for bank holiday Monday
OL,6,FA UK heatwave is officially recorded
OL,7,Fwhen an area experiences at least
OL,8,Fthree consecutive days with
OL,9,Ftemperatures meeting or exceeding the
OL,10,Fregion's heatwave threshold.
OL,12,FThe current May temperature record
OL,13,Fstands at 32.8C, recorded in Camden
OL,14,FSquare, London, in 1922.
OL,16,FThe warmest day recorded in the UK so
OL,17,Ffar this year was 26.6C at Kew Gardens
OL,18,Fin south-west London in April.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
